        >
          Lorem ipsum
        </h2>
        <p
          class="sectionMediumText text-accent font-robot font-normal"
        >
          In a rapidly evolving digital landscape, EXP Group is at the forefront
          of technological advancement. We are committed to building the future
          by writing robust and scalable code that powers the next generation of
          software.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="block">
        <p
          class="sectionLargeText text-davyGray font-robot my-3 lg:my-0 lg:mb-4"
        >
          Our Mission
        </p>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
